## WaveMaker Studio Conventions

- Login: PlatformDB REST (`wavemaker.ai` domains) or WaveMaker form login (`wavemakeronline.com`)
- Preview shortcut: `Ctrl+Alt+R`
- Preview 2-phase build: outer 8-step + inner rn-bundle 3-step
- Drag-drop: JS slow-mouse approach (mouse.down → 600ms → 20 step move → mouse.up)
- After dialog close: canvas selection resets to `page_content1` — must re-click widget
- Widget naming: `{prefix}{N}` (e.g., `button1`, `label1`)
- Preview testID pattern: `{prefix}{N}_{subElement}` (e.g., `button1_caption`)

